{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"categories":1,"event_categories":27},[2,9,15,21],{"id":3,"attributes":4},1,{"slug":5,"name":6,"description":7,"createdAt":8,"updatedAt":8},"nutrition","營養隨筆",null,"2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"id":10,"attributes":11},2,{"slug":12,"name":13,"description":7,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"reflection","感悟隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.692Z",{"id":16,"attributes":17},3,{"slug":18,"name":19,"description":7,"createdAt":20,"updatedAt":20},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-12T02:39:02.697Z",{"id":22,"attributes":23},4,{"slug":24,"name":25,"description":7,"createdAt":26,"updatedAt":26},"spiritual","心靈勵志","2023-02-12T02:39:02.698Z",[28,33,38,43,47,52],{"id":3,"attributes":29},{"name":30,"slug":31,"description":7,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"讀書會","book-sharing","2023-02-12T02:38:55.939Z",{"id":16,"attributes":34},{"name":35,"slug":36,"description":7,"createdAt":37,"updatedAt":37},"文化導賞","cultural","2023-02-12T02:38:55.943Z",{"id":22,"attributes":39},{"name":40,"slug":41,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"遊山玩水","hiking","2023-02-12T02:38:55.946Z",{"id":44,"attributes":45},5,{"name":46,"slug":18,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"健體運動",{"id":48,"attributes":49},6,{"name":50,"slug":5,"description":7,"createdAt":51,"updatedAt":51},"活學營養","2023-02-12T02:38:55.947Z",{"id":10,"attributes":53},{"name":54,"slug":55,"description":7,"createdAt":56,"updatedAt":57},"名人面對面","be-our-guest","2023-02-12T02:38:55.942Z","2023-03-08T13:16:12.875Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/categories?","http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/event-categories?"]},"slash":"always"},{"type":"data","data":[{"id":1,"attributes":2},193,{"title":3,"excerpt":4,"content":5,"slug":6,"createdAt":7,"updatedAt":7,"author":8,"categories":9,"tags":17,"image":38,"related_posts":39},"筋長一寸，壽延十年",null,"\n\n俗語謂「筋長一寸，壽延十年」，先不要說是否壽延十年，但柔軟度高，至少可降低身體受傷或出現痛症的機會率💪。\n\n柔軟度指的是關節及周邊肌肉與韌帶能夠活動的最大範圍。當我們長時間保持同一姿勢，某些肌肉會長期處於疲勞緊繃或伸展無力狀態；尤其是若我們長時間姿勢不良，更會加劇肌肉不平衡的狀況😖，久而久之降低身體的柔軟度。\n\n不要以為柔軟度只是單單站立彎腰時摸不到腳趾啊，若情況變壞，蹲低綁鞋帶、舉手握巴士扶手、洗頭、穿衣服等日常生活細節也可能無法輕鬆完成😳。所以千萬不要待痛症出現時，才關注柔軟度的重要性呢！\n\n此外，柔軟度原來與心血管健康息息相關。據《美國心臟與循環系統》雜誌刊登的研究結果：「健康的血管具有彈性，而彈性有助於緩解血壓。筋很硬的時候，不僅肌肉伸縮困難，血管也不易伸展，容易引發各種心血管疾病。 」❤️ 通過伸展運動改善身體柔軟度，對改善中老年人的動脈硬化也有幫助呢！\n\n建議大家每週至少進行3次伸展運動，而每次運動後都記得要做伸展動作呢！伸展拉筋時有以下要點：\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟 有一點張力的感覺即可，避免過度伸展或強行拉扯；\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟 漸進式、緩慢地伸展，不要把肌肉剎那間推到極限；\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟 靜態伸展時，每次伸展時間約在15-30秒之間，每個動作反覆2-3次\n\n如欲了解更多，歡迎觀看《大鵬展翅》影片 https:\u002F\u002Ffb.watch\u002F4FnouNHo3v\u002F  。","stretching-210604","2021-04-06T00:00:00.000Z",{"data":4},{"data":10},[11],{"id":12,"attributes":13},3,{"slug":14,"name":15,"description":4,"createdAt":16,"updatedAt":16},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-12T02:39:02.697Z",{"data":18},[19,24,29,34],{"id":20,"attributes":21},231,{"name":22,"createdAt":23,"updatedAt":23},"柔軟度","2023-02-12T03:32:01.398Z",{"id":25,"attributes":26},232,{"name":27,"createdAt":28,"updatedAt":28},"拉筋","2023-02-12T03:32:01.399Z",{"id":30,"attributes":31},241,{"name":32,"createdAt":33,"updatedAt":33},"伸展","2023-02-12T03:32:01.403Z",{"id":35,"attributes":36},242,{"name":37,"createdAt":33,"updatedAt":33},"心血管健康",{"data":4},{"data":40},[]],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/posts?populate[author]=true&populate[categories]=true&populate[tags]=true&populate[image]=true&populate[related_posts]=true&filters[slug][$eq]=stretching-210604"],"params":["slug"]}}]}